title: WinFastPVR2_setup_20352
description:
The Leadtek WinFast PVR2 application allows you to view and record live TV or video, and playback recorded TV or video in a picture-in-picture (PIP) style, as well as control all available functions.This program is a powerful and easy-to-use application to provide the most feature-rich video/audio entertainment.


Latest version (31-01-2013). Works great with Windows 8.
